cat << EOF
Etox is a typesetting and text layout library based on Evas.  Etox 
helps you when it comes to displaying, moving, resizing, layering,
clipping, aligning, and coloring fonts in different styles.  It also
provides facilites for multi-line text layout, as well as obstacle
wrapping.
EOF
